Package: superlda
Type: Package
Title: A package to estimate supervised, generative models of text.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2018-06-08
Author: Travis G. Coan
Maintainer: Travis G. Coan <t.coan@exeter.ac.uk>
Description: An implementation of supervised (or labeled) and semi-supervised 
    latent Dirichlet allocation (LDA). It estimates word and topic probability
    distributions using collasped Gibbs sampling. It also includes a handful
    of functions to assess topic results and methods to infer topics in unseen
    documents.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.4)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.18), RcppArmadillo (>= 0.8.600.0)
LinkingTo: 
    Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Encoding: UTF-8
